description: This charming 2-bedroom unit is a true gem, offering every imaginable amenity and exquisite architectural detail. Enjoy your cozy fireplace and create a welcoming atmosphere while entertaining your guests. Hot water heater was installed in approx. 2018, washer/dryer 2022, & flooring 2022. The private deck is perfect for enjoying warm New England summer days. Nestled in a classic brick rowhouse in South Boston's sought-after City Point, this home is just three blocks from both M Street Beach and the Causeway. The building has been meticulously maintained, with a recent large-scale repointing project enhancing its classic exterior. Elegant recessed lighting, in-unit laundry, interior brick character, & basement storage add to the convenience and appeal. This move-in-ready home is located in a vibrant neighborhood, allowing you to enjoy the best of South Boston with its nightlife, entertainment, & restaurants. Commuters dream with access to Route 93 or bus to downtown, a must see!
